<view class="_div"><view class="container _div"><view class="page-header _div"><view class="_h3">生辰八字查询</view></view><view class="input-group date col-md-5 .hidden-xs _div"><label class="input-group-addon _span">出生日期</label><input class="yh-nostyle-input" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','birthday','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{birthday}}" bindinput="__e"/><label class="input-group-btn _span"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['calc']]]]}}" class="btn btn-default" bindtap="__e">查看八字</button></label></view><view id="usage" class="_div">使用说明：<view class="_ul"><view class="_li">出生日期精确到小时即可</view><view class="_li">出生日期须在公历1900-2100年之间</view></view></view><block wx:if="{{showCaclResult}}"><view class="col-md-6 _div" style="padding-left:0;"><view class="vspace _div"></view><view class="panel panel-success _div" id="result"><view class="panel-heading _div"><view class="panel-title _h3">生辰八字</view></view><view class="panel-body _div"><view class="_div"><label>阳历：</label><label class="_span">{{o_solar}}</label></view><view class="_div"><label>阴历：</label><label class="_span">{{o_lunar}}</label></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['showSxLuck']]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="_div"><label>生肖：</label><label class="_span">{{"属"+o_animal}}</label></view><block wx:if="{{SxLuckShow}}"><view class="yh-nostyle-tip _div"><view class="_div"><rich-text nodes="{{SxLuck}}"></rich-text></view></view></block><view class="_div"><label>八字：</label><label class="_span">{{o_eight}}</label></view><view class="_div"><label>五行：</label><label class="_span">{{o_five}}</label></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['showXiyongTip']]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="_div"><label>喜用：</label><label class="_span">{{o_xiyong}}</label></view><block wx:if="{{XiyongTipShow}}"><view class="yh-nostyle-tip _div">喜用神的计算是基于平衡，同类五行和异类五行的平衡。一般是缺补旺抑。<view class="_p"></view>同类五行：指日柱天干的五行，加上其的相生五行。比如日柱天干是“木”的话，水生木，木和水是同类五行，另外三个是异类五行。<view class="_p"></view>同类五行能量强于异类五行，则是常说的生辰八字偏旺，相反则是偏弱。<view class="_p"></view>八字旺，分为正常旺以及特殊格局，如果是正常旺，用“旺则抑，弱则扶”原理即可。<view class="_p"></view>如果是特殊的旺，无法抑制，只能顺从。<view class="_p"></view>见下例。<view class="_p"></view><view class="yh-nostyle-tip2 _div">附：五行相生相克关系表：<view class="_p"></view>相生：木生火/火生土/土生金/金生水/水生木<view class="_p"></view>相克：水克火/火克金/金克木/木克土/土克水<view class="_p"></view></view></view></block></view><view class="vspace _div"></view></view></view></block><view class="_p"></view><view class="_div"><view class="yh-nostyle-title2 _li">最新推出：以天为单位查询 ( ↓↓↓ )</view></view><view class="input-group date col-md-5 .hidden-xs _div"><label class="input-group-addon _span">出生日期</label><input class="yh-nostyle-input" type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','birthday2','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{birthday2}}" bindinput="__e"/><label class="input-group-btn _span"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['calc_oneday_show']]]]}}" class="btn btn-default" bindtap="__e">查看全天</button></label></view><block wx:if="{{showAllDay}}"><view class="col-md-6 _div" style="padding-left:0;"><view class="vspace _div"></view><view class="panel panel-success _div"><view class="panel-heading _div"><view class="panel-title _h3">详情列表</view></view><view class="panel-body _div"><view class="_div"><label class="_span">{{o_solar2}}</label></view><view class="_div"><label class="_span">{{o_lunar2}}</label></view><block wx:for="{{items}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="__i0__"><view class="_li">{{''+item.lino+''}}<view class="_p"></view>{{'八字： '+item.eight+''}}<view class="_p"></view>{{'五行： '+item.five+''}}<view class="_p"></view>{{''+item.xiyong+''}}<view class="_p"></view></view></block></view><view class="vspace _div"></view></view></view></block></view></view>